item.title: Crafts!!
item.description: Crafts from over the years Here are some of the things I’ve made from the past couple of years that I’m probably the most proud of :-) Paintings/calligraphy a painting for a service event (2017) A painting for a mentor (1 of 2) (2016) A painting for a mentor (2 of 2) (2016) A holiday card made for a friend (2016) Embroidery A thank you gift for a friend headed to Texas State (2016)

item.title: Python
item.description: Python discussion This is the blog post that is dedicated to Python and what we’ve learned in class. The thing I most enjoyed about Python this semester was what we learned for homework 11 where our task was to use regular expressions in python to match (and return) the requested parts in each. I just really enjoyed the process of looking for patterns in the strings that could ultimately be used in the re.
